      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.JAvuKoQyqneaCgif]{Flamewalker}</p>\n<p>When you perform a charge, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to take on a fiery aspect as you move, increasing your speed by 10 feet until the end of your turn. At 8th level, when you use this ability, you also gain concealment (20% miss chance) against all attacks made against you during the charge and until the beginning of your next turn. At 13th level, this miss chance increases to 40% and lasts until the end of your next turn.</p>"
